trans-unit.source: Represents a line used to group items of a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip" /> or the drop-down items of a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.MenuStrip" /> or <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ContextMenuStrip" /> or other <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripDropDown" /> control.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma linha usada para agrupar itens de um <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip" /> ou os itens de lista suspensa de um <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.MenuStrip" /> ou <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ContextMenuStrip" /> ou outro controle <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripDropDown" />.

trans-unit.source: Use a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSeparator> to group related items on a menu or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>.
trans-unit.target: Use um <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSeparator> para agrupar itens relacionados em um menu ou <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSeparator> is automatically spaced and oriented horizontally or vertically to accord with its container.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSeparator> automaticamente espaçados e orientada horizontal ou verticalmente de acordo com seu contêiner.

trans-unit.source: You can add a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSeparator> at design time by choosing it from a drop-down list.
trans-unit.target: Você pode adicionar um <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSeparator> em tempo de design selecionando-a em uma lista suspensa.

trans-unit.source: However, you can also automatically create a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSeparator> by typing a hyphen (-) in either the designer template node or in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItemCollection.Add%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: No entanto, você pode criar automaticamente uma <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSeparator> digitando um hífen (-) no nó designer de modelo ou no <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItemCollection.Add%2A> método.
